dct_title_s: 广州导游图 = Guangzhou tourist map
dct_description_sm: Ancillary maps on recto: Original site of the Peasant Movement Institute -- Memorial garden to the martyrs in the Guangzhou uprising -- Huanghuagang Mausoleum of the 72 martyrs -- Yuexiu Park -- Guangzhou Zoo. On verso: Sketch maps of terminal buildings of the Baiyun airport -- Foshan City]-- Zhaoqing City. Selected buildings are shown pictorially. Includes text and tourist information. "Book no. 120114-1188".
